casebody.data:
No. 168,

Misc.

Elfbrandt v. Russell et al. W. Edward Morgan for petitioner. Darrell F. Smith, Attorney General of Arizona, Philip M. Haggerty, Assistant Attorney General, and Norman E. Green for respondents.

Sup. Ct. Ariz. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. The case is transferred to the appellate docket.
